# Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)

Instead of asking the LLM directly:

```
Question

↓

LLM

↓

Answer
```

NetworkGPT performs:

```
Question

↓

Embedding

↓

Vector Search

↓

Relevant Cisco Docs

↓

LLM

↓

Grounded Answer
```

This greatly improves factual accuracy and reduces hallucinations.

